{"tid":2402884,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"開左個加拿大人tg - group","createTime":"2021-02-10T17:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T08:07:31.000Z","uid":36861,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b67bcc65111d0a8a64ec63f402a1c1862b753194","tid":2402884,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/canada_hker_main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcanada_hker_main&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=55c2c41c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/canada_hker_main</a><br />\n我地多數會係多倫多GTA約埋一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊食野行山睇戲shopping<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 如果真係有心過黎, 可以入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大溫地區都welcome, 我地主會提供資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 同睇你地留意下你地當地想留意既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://t.me/canada_hker_main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcanada_hker_main&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=55c2c41c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/canada_hker_main</a></strong><br />\n(只限黃, 走藍走豬please.) (本群極黃, 入群沒有要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但如果藍既會屌完再踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 入群前請三思而後行。如果你係一個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 唔好入.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n搵工, 搵屋, 搵學校, 搵工, 之類都可以問下, 答到都會答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, group 入邊有唔同地區既多倫多人同溫哥華人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。希望幫到你地。<br />\n<br />\n另外我同某些連登仔(古力巴)打算遲下搞個實體的多倫多香港人社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 幫大家投入新家園<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 如果大家反應好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我地就搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啦 (入左group可以有poll問下大家意見, 唔關事既可以唔投), 需要少量<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 同義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 如果你地過到黎又得忙, welcome黎幫手(主要係幫人搵下有關資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 教下人點買餸, 反教會, 邊區好D, 搵學校, 呢樣個樣), 詳情遲下開個website<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問大家意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/canada_hker_main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcanada_hker_main&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=55c2c41c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/canada_hker_main</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>有無需要搞個香港人社區?</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有, 可以幫下同路人, 學生哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 有小朋友既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單身狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等等。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無, 晒氣晒時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 過左加拿大自食其力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 無本事唔好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n比下意見。"},{"pid":"12d454a788e84779884c0314d857a7d0ecd485ef","tid":2402884,"uid":41642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"QC可唔可以入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"